-v=\"crystal\">Кристалл<\u002Fbutton>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n  <\u002Fdiv>\n  <div class=\"fx-row\"><span>Живой неон по контурам<\u002Fspan><div class=\"fx-sw\" data-fx=\"fx-neon\"><\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n  <div class=\"fx-row\"><span>Блик и наклон карточек<\u002Fspan><div class=\"fx-sw\" data-fx=\"fx-tilt\"><\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n  <div class=\"fx-row\"><span>Свечение у курсора<\u002Fspan><div class=\"fx-sw\" data-fx=\"fx-cursor\"><\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n  <div class=\"fx-row\"><span>Частицы и искры<\u002Fspan><div class=\"fx-sw\" data-fx=\"fx-particles\"><\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n  <div class=\"fx-row\"><span>Лепестки сакуры<\u002Fspan><div class=\"fx-sw\" data-fx=\"fx-petals\"><\u002Fdiv><\u002Fdiv>\n  <div class=\"fx-slider\"><span>Интенсивность свечения<\u002Fspan><input type=\"range\" id=\"fxGlow\" min=\"0.3\" max=\"1.6\" step=\"0.05\" value=\"1\"><\u002Fdiv>\n<\u002Fdiv>\n\n<div id=\"capture\">\n  <header class=\"toolbar\">\n    <div class=\"brand\">\n      <div class=\"mark\">殿<\u002Fdiv>\n      <div class=\"txt\"><b>Аниме Тир-лист<\u002Fb><span>личный канон<\u002Fspan><\u002Fdiv>\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n    <div class=\"tb-spacer\"><\u002Fdiv>\n    <div class=\"search\">\n      <svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><circle cx=\"11\" cy=\"11\" r=\"7\"><\u002Fcircle><line x1=\"21\" y1=\"21\" x2=\"16.65\" y2=\"16.65\"><\u002Fline><\u002Fsvg>\n      <input type=\"text\" id=\"searchInput\" placeholder=\"Поиск тайтла…\" autocomplete=\"off\" spellcheck=\"false\">\n    <\u002Fdiv>\n    <div class=\"seg\" id=\"viewSeg\">\n      <button data-view=\"grid\" class=\"on\" title=\"Сетка постеров\"><svg viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\"><rect x=\"3\" y=\"3\" width=\"7\" height=\"7\" rx=\"1.5\"><\u002Frect><rect x=\"14\" y=\"3\" width=\"7\" height=\"7\" rx=\"1.5\"><\u002Frect><rect x=\"3\" y=\"14\" width=\"7\" height=\"7\" rx=\"1.5\"><\u002Frect><rect x=\"14\" y=\"14\" width=\"7\" height=\"7\" rx